```

This adds ~15 security headers in one line including CSP, HSTS, and X-Frame-Options.

---

### 4. No Rate Limiting (OWASP A04: Insecure Design)

Any endpoint can be hammered without restriction, enabling brute-force attacks and denial-of-service.

**Recommendation:**

```js
